Click the link above or open the .twbx file in your local environment

Explore with filters, tooltips, and drill-downs

Dive into each dashboard tab to understand trends and insights

📌 Outcomes & Learnings

Identified high-risk customer segments by age & employment type

Highlighted branches with elevated default rates

Revealed gaps in KYC/document verification compliance

Created a cohesive risk-monitoring dashboard for decision-makers

